99 An Act relating to state procurement; creating the
Procurement Protection Act of 2026; defining terms;
1100 prohibiting certain entities from entering into
contracts with certain companies; requiring certain
1111 disclosure statements; providing penalties; providing
exceptions to certain prohibitions; providing for
1122 noncodification; providing for codification; and
providing an effective date.
1133
1144
